<BYLINE>
   By RODERICK ORAM, Consumer Industries Editor
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
BAT Industries and Turkey's state tobacco company, Tekel, are to form a
joint venture managed by the UK group to make cigarettes in Turkey. BAT will
invest a substantial sum to turn Tekel's plant at Akhisar into a modern
